txt.en: 'The Lumber-mill allows for woodworkers to ply their craft and create anything from boards, to bows, to exquisite instruments. The better the quality and tools available on the workbench, the greater quality of item can be produced upon it. We can update and upgrade our Lumber-mill with a superior workbench that will allow us to craft the finest of goods.'
